ust state, F × HT × z2 = full mechanical ceremony at L3/L1 + 4+ above-baseline visible-deliberation moves above from-scratch baseline. This Statement provides personal-context grounding (S80 instance / time / post-S79 fresh-engagement / JK auth + §3 catch + (a) ratification timestamps), engagement-trace structured rationale (substrate authoring at commit dd48083 + Content-Hash computation methodology + initial substrate gap on z-enumeration caught by JK §3 substrate-review at 11:46 AEST + drafter-lean (a) reasoning for in-place revision-without-Session-Nonce-burn since spec files unchanged + bias #28 sub-shape recurrence-fire on `mcap nonce --combine` output-format-assumption-mismatch in finalization script v1 fixed at v2), style independence (own-voice composition diverging from CHANGELOG entry framing and from canonical substance text being placed), and substantive Reservations below. The from-scratch authoring of this revised Statement post-§3-catch is itself a fresh authoring act per `feedback_mcap_statement_authorship.md` absolute rule; the prior substrate Statement at commit c157afb is superseded by this revision at the substrate-revision commit (still pre-signing, so no re-attestation issue).
